&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=&quot; font-family:'Roboto'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Roboto','sans-serif';&quot;&gt;[1] Yetton, B. D., et al. (2016). Automatic detection of rapid eye movements (REMs): A machine learning approach.     &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Roboto','sans-serif'; font-style:italic;&quot;&gt;Journal of neuroscience methods&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Roboto','sans-serif';&quot;&gt;,     &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Roboto','sans-serif'; font-style:italic;&quot;&gt;259&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Roboto','sans-serif';&quot;&gt;, 72–82.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:10pt;&quot;&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Roboto','sans-serif';&quot;&gt;[2] Agarwal, R., et al. (2005). Detection of rapid-eye movements in sleep studies.     &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Roboto','sans-serif'; font-style:italic;&quot;&gt;IEEE Transactions on biomedical engineering&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Roboto','sans-serif';&quot;&gt;,     &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Roboto','sans-serif'; font-style:italic;&quot;&gt;52&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-family:'Roboto','sans-serif';&quot;&gt;(8), 1390–1396.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
